{"id":1191,"date":"2016-04-19T13:41:22","date_gmt":"2016-04-19T12:41:22","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.edlab.org.uk\/?p=1191"},"modified":"2016-04-20T08:27:19","modified_gmt":"2016-04-20T07:27:19","slug":"student-resource-pop-art-andy-warhol-creative-craft","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/mcrblogs.co.uk\/edlab\/student-resource-pop-art-andy-warhol-creative-craft\/","title":{"rendered":"Student Resource: Pop Art Andy Warhol Creative Craft"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Step by step instructions to run an activity exploring Pop Art using an Andy Warhol inspired approach.<\/p>\n<p>Before starting, gather children into groups of 4.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\" size-height360 wp-image-1193 aligncenter\" src=\"http:\/\/mcrblogs.co.uk\/edlab\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/64\/2016\/04\/warhol-1-480x360.jpg\" alt=\"warhol 1\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" \/><\/p>\n<p><!--more--><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>Then Gather equipment. This includes:\n<ul>\n<li>A3 card<\/li>\n<li>Black paint<\/li>\n<li>Paint pot<\/li>\n<li>Paint brush<\/li>\n<li>Scissors<\/li>\n<li>Pen to draw round hand<\/li>\n<li>Glue sticks<\/li>\n<li>A5 paper<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/li>\n<li>Get each child to select a piece of coloured A5 card to go in one corner of the large A3 card. This will create a college of bright colours which will be the background of the picture.<\/li>\n<li>Then get the child to select a different coloured piece of card.<\/li>\n<li>Once chosen get a black felt tip pen and get the child to draw round there hand.<\/li>\n<li>Once done then cut out the shape.<\/li>\n<li>Stick the cut out hand print on to the child\u2019s selected colour card.<\/li>\n<li>Get a paint brush and black paint for them to then paint there hand over the colour card hand print.<\/li>\n<li>This will then create an Andy Warhol style of art<\/li>\n<li>It would be a great idea after to create a Big college of the pupils crafts on the wall. This would look really effective and colourful for everyone to see.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-height360 wp-image-1194\" src=\"http:\/\/mcrblogs.co.uk\/edlab\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/64\/2016\/04\/warhol2-556x360.jpg\" alt=\"warhol2\" width=\"556\" height=\"360\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Alternative option:<\/h3>\n<p>If you did not want to the children to draw round there hand and cut out, then they could paint there hand with another colour and press it on the paper. Followed by the Black Hand print to give it the Andy Warhol effect.<\/p>\n<p>This document as a Word Document\u00a0 &#8211; <a href=\"http:\/\/mcrblogs.co.uk\/edlab\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/64\/2016\/04\/Pop-art-Andy-Warhol-Creative-Craft.docx\">Pop art Andy Warhol Creative Craft<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Step by step instructions to run an activity exploring Pop Art using an Andy Warhol inspired approach. Before starting, gather children into groups of 4.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":29,"featured_media":1194,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[41,44],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v15.6.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/mcrblogs.co.uk\/edlab\/student-resource-pop-art-andy-warhol-creative-craft\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Student Resource: Pop Art Andy Warhol Creative Craft - EdLab MMU\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Step by step instructions to run an activity exploring Pop Art using an Andy Warhol inspired approach. Before starting, gather children into groups of 4.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/mcrblogs.co.uk\/edlab\/student-r